OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FA learner driver has been jailed for
OL,7,Fnearly five years after killing three
OL,8,Ffriends in a crash.
OL,10,FLoy, 19, pleaded guilty to causing the
OL,11,Fdeath of three boys by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving on the A711 near Dumfries on
OL,13,F16 March 2022. Loy has been sentenced
OL,14,Fto four years and eight months.
OL,16,FThe three teenagers Tyler Johnston,
OL,17,FIan Cannon and Finlay Johns, all 16,
OL,18,Fdied at the scene.
