OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FThree men who were in a Honda CR-V
OL,7,Ftravelling on the other side of the
OL,8,Froad, also suffered serious injuries
OL,9,Fshortly after midnight. They were
OL,10,Fadhering to the 60mph speed limit.
OL,12,FLoy, who was 17 at the time of the
OL,13,Fincident, was disqualified from
OL,14,Fdriving for eight years and banned
OL,15,Ffrom the road until passing an
OL,16,Fextended driving test is passed, at
OL,17,Fthe High Court in Glasgow.
OL,19,FJudge Lord Harrower said that "no
OL,20,Fsentence can alleviate the anguish" of
OL,21,Fthe victim's families.
