OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FHe said: "Your actual speed is unknown
OL,7,Fbut the collision split it in two.
OL,9,F"The investigating officer was of the
OL,10,Fopinion that you must have been going
OL,11,Fmuch faster than the other car, which
OL,12,Fwas driving at 60mph. I conclude you
OL,13,Fmust have been driving in excess of
OL,14,Fthe speed limit.
OL,16,F"Ian Cannon posted a message saying he
OL,17,Fwas scared because you were swerving
OL,18,Fall over the place and you were a
OL,19,Fterrible driver and flooring it."
