OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FLoy's sentence was reduced due to
OL,7,Fchanges on Scottish sentencing
OL,8,Fguidelines for under-25s. The changes
OL,9,Fwere introduced the same year of the
OL,10,Fcrash in 2022.
OL,12,FSentencing, Lord Harrower said: "Three
OL,13,Fyoung lives have been lost. Three
OL,14,Fother individuals sustained serious
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,F"You sustained serious injuries. The
OL,18,Fdeceased were all friends and you have
OL,19,Fshown remorse.
