OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,F"The social work report highlights
OL,7,Fconcerns raised in psychological
OL,8,Fassessments carried out between the
OL,9,Fages of 12 and 17 years old."
OL,11,FDefending, Donald Findlay KC, said Loy
OL,12,Fhad no recollection of the crash due
OL,13,Fto a head injury.
OL,15,FMr Findlay said: "It was quite moving
OL,16,Fwhen he said that if he could take the
OL,17,Fplace of them, he would have rather it
OL,18,Fhad been him."
