OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FPsychologist Professor Gary MacPherson
OL,7,Fassessed Loy and found he was
OL,8,F"immature".
OL,10,FMr Findlay suggested he may have
OL,11,Fwanted to "endear himself" to his peer
OL,12,Fgroup and "impress" his friends, the
OL,13,Fcourt heard.
OL,15,FThe court heard that Mr Cannon had
OL,16,Fsent a Snapchat message prior to the
OL,17,Fcrash saying he was "scared" because
OL,18,FLoy was a "terrible driver and
OL,19,Fflooring it".
