OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FThe court heard that 19-year-old Loy
OL,7,Fwas speeding in his Honda Civic when
OL,8,Fhe lost control and crashed into
OL,9,Fanother car.
OL,11,FHe was driving on a provisional
OL,12,Flicence, carrying three friends in the
OL,13,Fcar at the time of the crash, who all
OL,14,Fdied at the scene.
OL,16,FLord Harrower said he would have given
OL,17,FLoy a seven-year sentence had he not
OL,18,Fentered an early guilty plea.
