OL,6,FHe said: "In my view, there is no
OL,7,Falternative to a substantial custodial
OL,8,Fsentence - albeit substantially less
OL,9,Fthan for an older person."
OL,11,FMoira Orr, procurator fiscal for
OL,12,Fhomicide and major crime, says it is a
OL,13,F"truly tragic incident".
OL,15,FShe said: "Jake Loy chose to drive his
OL,16,Fvehicle despite not holding a full
OL,17,Flicence and being an inexperienced
OL,18,Froad user.
