OL,3,CJake Loy sentenced to four years after
OL,4,Ckilling three friends in crash
OL,6,FPolice Scotland road policing Chief
OL,7,FInspector Lorraine Napier said: "I
OL,8,Fwould like to pay tribute to the
OL,9,Ffamilies and friends of the three
OL,10,Fyoung men who lost their lives in this
OL,11,Fcrash, and thank everyone who worked
OL,12,Fso diligently to bring this case to a
OL,13,Fconclusion.
OL,15,F"No conviction or sentence will ever
OL,16,Freflect the impact the crash had on
OL,17,Fthe families and friends of Ian, Tyler
OL,18,Fand Finlay, but I hope it brings some
OL,19,Fmeasure of closure."
